<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <title>Welcome to Readr</title>
    <style>
      body {
        font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
        line-height: 1.6;
        color: #333;
      }
      .container {
        max-width: 600px;
        margin: auto;
        padding: 20px;
      }
      .header {
        background-color: #4a90e2;
        color: white;
        text-align: center;
        padding: 20px;
      }
      .content {
        padding: 20px;
      }
      .button {
        display: inline-block;
        background-color: #4a90e2;
        color: white;
        padding: 10px 20px;
        text-decoration: none;
        border-radius: 5px;
      }
      .expire-note {
        color: #888;
        font-size: 0.9em;
      }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <div class="container">
      <div class="header">
        <h1>Welcome to Readr</h1>
      </div>
      <div class="content">
        <p>Hi <%= username %>,</p>

        <p>
          We're thrilled to have you join Readr as a writer, Your account is now active, and you're ready to explore a world of articles, and stories.
        </p>

        <p>Here's what you can do next:</p>
        <ul>
          <li>Create your first Article</li>
        </ul>

        <p>
          <a href="<%= verificationUrl %>" class="button">Verify Email</a>
        </p>

        <p class="expire-note">This verification link will expire in <%= linkExpiration %>.</p>

        <p>Happy writing!<br />The Readr Team</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>
